Yeye nayaleke yehile na yatende yanogile, yapate na kuwinza tindiwalo.
Kwaviya Mndewa kawalola wanhu wanogile, na magutwi yake yotegeleza nhosa zawo, mbali Mndewa kawamanyaga wanhu wotenda yehile."
Munhu yelihi yoyodaha kumtendelani yehile one mwahasang'hanila kutenda yanogile?
Mbali hata one nolondeka kugazigwa kwa ichimu cha kutenda yanogile, mbali Mulungu kamtemelani mate. Mleche kuwadumba wanhu wawo, wala sekemudumbe.
Mbali mumtogole Chilisito Mndewa muna imizoyo yenu. Muwe mwelile siku zose kuwa goya kumwidika munhu yoyose yoyawauzani kwa ichimu cha uhuwilo womuli nawo,
Mbali muvimanye kuwa na magesa yanogile. Muleke kutenda yehile, muladi wanhu waja wowolonga mbuli zihile kusonhela mweye na kutenda yanogile fana wanhu wohuwila Chilisito, wawone chinyala kwa ichimu cha maligo yawo.
Kwaviya muhavu kugazika kwa ichimu cha kutenda yanogile, one Mulungu yahalonda, kufosa kugazika kwa ichimu cha kutenda yehile.
Kwaviya Chilisito mwenyewo kagazigwa na kagazigwa kwa ichimu cha uhasanyi wake, na kagazigwa kamwe muhala, munhu yanogile kagazigwa kwa ichimu cha wanhu wehile, muladi yawagoneke mweye kwa Mulungu. Kaminigwa lukuli mbali muhe kamdita kuwa mgima.
na kahita kuwapetela waja muhe wowakalile muna ichifungo.
